  .container
    .half-slider-row
      .copy.copy--left
        %h2.leader Meet
        %h1 Our Grads
        %p We've graduated over 300 beginners into their dream jobs as junior developers. Some were looking for a career change, others to define themselves.
        .button-row
          %p
            %a.button--horizontal Read Grad Stories
      .slider
        .slider-content
          %figure.with-caption
            .image
